general_info.Scenario Description: Implementation of a) a visitable green roof (NBS1 and NBS2) on top of the schools's multi-purpose building and the school entrance roof supported by rainwater harvesting (RWH) (1 roof) and b) a low green shelter (NBS3) at the east side of the school supported by greywater recycling (GWR) that is also utilised for students' WC
